    "description": "光标很容易丢失——尤其是在快节奏游戏或明亮场景中。无论是在游戏还是 Windows 应用中，都可以自定义和增强你的光标。<br><br>非常适合 MOBA、MMO、RPG 和 ARPG 游戏。同样适用于演示、直播和日常桌面使用。<br><br>让这个光标工具成为你的游戏利器！😎<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >提升可见性</h2>让微小的光标变大、更加醒目。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/c297f194cf9bb65d32eaea658b040e27.poster.avif?t=1771833049\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/c297f194cf9bb65d32eaea658b040e27.webm?t=1771833049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/c297f194cf9bb65d32eaea658b040e27.mp4?t=1771833049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >增强现有光标</h2>在保留原有风格的同时增强光标大小和发光效果。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/d00cb916c6d8c3a230000c126e1836da.poster.avif?t=1771833049\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/d00cb916c6d8c3a230000c126e1836da.webm?t=1771833049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/d00cb916c6d8c3a230000c126e1836da.mp4?t=1771833049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >添加特效</h2>缩放、十字和光环等效果可在复杂画面中提升清晰度。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/a315152524545e0a93b4bd5427b2a1cc.poster.avif?t=1771833049\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/a315152524545e0a93b4bd5427b2a1cc.webm?t=1771833049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/a315152524545e0a93b4bd5427b2a1cc.mp4?t=1771833049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >添加风格</h2>风格化与动画 3D 光标选项。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/ff2c8d458f99cd30f0875f97bc86bc28.poster.avif?t=1771833049\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/ff2c8d458f99cd30f0875f97bc86bc28.webm?t=1771833049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/ff2c8d458f99cd30f0875f97bc86bc28.mp4?t=1771833049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功能特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>全局支持</strong>: 支持游戏和 Windows 应用。<br></li><li><strong>尺寸</strong>: 调整新旧光标大小。<br></li><li><strong>颜色</strong>: 丰富颜色选择，包括反色。<br></li><li><strong>特效</strong>: 添加缩放、十字、光环、发光和镜像效果。<br></li><li><strong>预设</strong>: 快速应用预设光标组合。<br></li><li><strong>创建</strong>: 内置编辑器支持普通和动画光标。<br></li><li><strong>性能</strong>: 轻量无负担，对性能影响极小。<br></li><li><strong>多样性</strong>: 提供多种基础与 3D 覆盖光标。<br></li><li><strong>社区</strong>: 通过 Steam 创意工坊分享和下载更多光标。<br></li><li><strong>趣味</strong>: 果冻物理效果！</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快速开始</h2>将鼠标悬停在要更改的光标上，按下 <strong>CTRL ALT C</strong> 打开选择界面，然后选择新的样式、大小和颜色。<br><strong>小技巧:</strong> 若要快速让所有光标更醒目，选择特殊的 <strong>全部</strong> 光标，然后增大尺寸或添加发光效果。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这不是作弊工具</h2>YoloMouse 类似其他辅助工具。它不会修改游戏，也不会提供任何游戏优势。已广泛加入白名单并经过代码签名，并定期在主流游戏中测试安全性。使用前请确认符合游戏的服务条款。",
